oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Tennessee State University
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Tennessee A & I State University's Tigersharks, Coached by Thomas H. "Friend" Hughes Took Six Out of Seven Meets, Set Six Records in the 400 Yard Medley, Broke Four Records in the 200 Yard Butterfly and Broke One Record in the 50-Yard Freestyle. They are Uncrowned Intercollegiate Champs.
